                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8208" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2046</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1091 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">柏越：装备红利的探索者，以标准解决非标准</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">PAYA: The Explorer of Equipment Dividends, Solving the Non-standard with Standards</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">徐艳梅，张亚楠，白振立，张绮炆</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国科学院大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">广州柏越机电设备有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">研发部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业家精神；数字化转型；自动化</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Entrepreneurship; Digital transformation; Automation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人口红利优势逐年降低是我国面临的重要问题之一，自动化、数字化是化解这一问题的有效途径。本案例讲述了一家高科技民营企业柏越，通过最新的数字孪生技术，打通控制柜设计端和生产端的链接，将技术工人密集型车间升级为自动化数字化车间，提升生产效率，用装备红利替代人口红利的故事。案例陈述了柏越公司从服务到生产再到服务的螺旋式发展过程。介绍了企业通过搭建数字化车间，开启电气标准化和程序标准化咨询服务新业务，实现自身数字化转型的同时助力装备制造中小企业共同发展，从而践行“帮助中小企业成为细分领域的‘隐形冠军’，将人口红利转变为装备红利”企业使命的前因后果。案例旨在帮助学员深入理解企业家精神、企业环境、数字化转型等理论概念及在现实中的相互作用关系。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The gradual reduction of demographic dividend is a significant challenge faced by China, but leveraging automation and digitalization emerges as an effective solution. This case presents the story of PAYA, a high-tech private enterprise that employs the latest digital twin technology to establish a seamless connection between the design end and production end of the control cabinet. This transformation enables the conversion of a labor-intensive workshop into an automated and digitized facility, resulting in enhanced production efficiency and the substitution of the demographic dividend with an equipment dividend. The case describes PAYA&#39;s spiral development process from service to production and then to service. It shows how the company, by establishing a digitalized workshop, opening a new business such as electrical standardization and program standardization consulting service. Through this endeavor, PAYA not only achieves its own digital transformation but also facilitates the collaborative growth of small and medium-sized enterprises in the equipment manufacturing industry. This exemplifies PAYA&#39;s mission to assist small and medium-sized enterprises in becoming &quot;hidden champions&quot; in specialized domains, thereby transforming the demographic dividend into an equipment dividend. The objective of this case is to provide students with a comprehensive understanding of theoretical concepts and practical activities related to entrepreneurship, business environments, and digital transformation.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》、《创新创业管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业家精神；企业环境分析（TOE理论)；企业数字化成熟度模型；</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-03</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
